column5: I will be at the show sometime in the early afternoon (all depends on my sons nap time) and am Looking forward to seeing everyone @ the show!   Gerritt.
Showing up around 1 and leaving in time to grab a bite and go to the game.  Geritt, I may see you at both events.  :-)

I'll be there, not sure what time yet.  I'm hoping to catch a couple of seminars, but don't think I'll make it for Dave Mercer  .  I'm also planning on going for wings after...just look for the yellow jacket  Maureen
i think i will be there when it opens and get out before the crowds get real bad...hope to see some of you guys there...cheers
Leaving here around 7am, hope to hit the show before it gets too busy then off to BPS afterwards.
We're heading down around noon, and probably going for wings after too!  Joey

I'm going in nice and early as I am registered in the Wild Turkey course put on by the OFAH. Supposed to get out sometime around 1, then hopefully wont spend too much money before I finally head for home...
